wp:comment.wp:comment_content:
I prefer using plain Java for this: 

MyApp#init() {

  ...

  Mounter.mount(this)

  ...

}

class Mounter {

  public static void mount(WebApplication app) {

     app.mountPage(...);

     ...

     app.mountResource(...);

     ...

   }

}

No need of external config files to be parsed. Code completion as much as possible. Full access to the APIs (root mapper, #mount(IRequestMapper), #mountResource, #mountPackage).
